1. Collection of Personal Information
Ori Wish Limited Gaming Platform is a subordinate service platform of Ori Wish Limited, aimed at providing more high-quality products and services. Under the permits of law, the use of our services may involve the collection and use of your Information on our services (including providing your Information to the service providers and the affiliated companies) according to the Personal Information Protection Act, in order to provide and improve our Services. And we ensure that all information collected would be kept strictly confidential when used.
As noted below and depending upon your particular use of the Services, we collect information from you, from third parties, and automatically through your use of our Services, some of which is required and some of which is optional.
To use the Services, we require you to register, by providing your email address and/or contact information, by creating an account directly with Ori Wish Limited, or by logging in through a third-party account (“Third Party Account”); when you do so, Ori Wish Limited collects the following required personal information:
