5. DISCLOSING INFORMATION
You acknowledge and authorize Ori Wish Limited to retain and store all the information you provide and place the information in one or more of the Company's databases. We will maintain a comprehensive control and protection to all information in accordance with strict standards of security and confidentiality, and will not disclose it to any third party, except for the following persons or organizations:
1) Employees in Ori Wish Limited who have received formal training in handling customer information and have authorization from the company.
2) Third-party service providers who provide support services. These providers must comply with the privacy standards of this Privacy Policy since they are bound to the agreement.
3) Any person who need to know the information based on applicable laws, government or regulations.
4) Any trustee or transferee who benefits from our company when there is a situation of company's business restructuring, reorganization or similar incident happening.
5) The person or organization that you make deal with through Ori Wish Limited platform services, such as payment services, banks, financial institutions, or other institutions.
6) If there is any of the following situations in Ori Wish Limited, we will retain the right to disclose your personal information to the specific person:
a) Ori Wish Limited has sufficient reasons to believe that to disclose your information is necessary for identifying or contacting you.
b) You violate the terms of Use of Ori Wish Limited website or products, your acts cause damage or interference to Ori Wish Limited website, rights, products, or other users, or the person who suffers damage or interference takes legal action against you.
c) Ori Wish Limited has sufficient reasons to believe that you are involved in fraud, or other illegal and default actions.
7) Any advertiser or any other site linked to Ori Wish Limited website you find may also collect your personal information, but this Privacy Policy does not apply to the advertisers or other websites, and can not control their behavior.
6. IMPACT OF NOT PROVIDING INFORMATION OR PROVIDING FALSE INFORMATION
1) When you join as a member of Ori Wish Limited website or apply for other services with the necessity to fill in your personal information, if the information you provide are reported by others to be untrue or Ori Wish Limited find that the information are insufficient to confirm the authenticity of your identity, Ori Wish Limited will have to suspend our services for you. After you make the correction, Ori Wish Limited will restore the services if we confirm the authenticity while not processing your request if we can not confirm.
2) When you join as a member of Ori Wish Limited website or apply for other services, there are some information which are optional to fill in. But this also means that you will not be able to use services or products that required registration or relevant information (such as "subscribe to the newsletter" and birthday benefit). Besides, if your account is assumed or your information are stolen, we will not be able to process your request because we can not confirm the authenticity of your identity from the unprovided or untrue information.
7. CHOICE OF USER
Ori Wish Limited will occasionally provide the latest news by e-mail to users or make communications without your request. If you do not wish to receive future messages without your request, you may contact our customer service by e-mail, and they will remove your name from the contact list of the messages above. We will only keep your contact details for the use to provide you with customer services, such as to notify you the latest discount, modifications of member services, etc.
8. INFORMATION COLLCETED USING COOKIES
We may use "Cookies " to collect users' information for services, which helps users to re-visit the website. A cookie is a small piece of text sent to your browser by the website you visit. It helps the website to remember the information about your visit, like your preferred language and other settings. That can make your next visit easier and the site more useful for you. Recently, the information collected by Cookies will be used to improve our services. The information provided from Ori Wish Limited services are based on an analysis of the company about the cumulative use of the services of users, and the data are organized and orchestrated. Cookies help you to login the application faster and more conveniently, meanwhile, preserving data between sessions.
You can change your browser options to stop automatically accepting Cookies without affecting the access to our company's website, but Cookies do make our services more convenient to use. Please note, however, that if you don't accept Cookies, it will make it complicated to use our services or you will need to input information for quite many times. Besides, you may not be able to access all portions or features of the Services.
